content: Hello, I'm looking for a reviewer or general feedback of my expect attribute implementation for RFC 2383. The PR #86024 has been laying around for a while and I was hoping that someone could support me with the final to-dos and open questions :upside_down:
Currently taking a look, I don't know this part of the codebase very well but hopefully I can find things that can move the PR forward
Thank you as well @Léo Lanteri Thauvin! Feel free to ask any questions in the PR :)
